          <h3 class="ipad-cost-title">We'll Match Any Local Repair Price</h3>
          <p class="ipad-cost-body">Found a lower price at another Winnipeg repair shop? We'll match it — so you don't overpay. No pressure. No hassle.</p>
          <a href="sms:2045009757?body=Hey%20Mobile%20Tech%20Lab!%20I%20want%20a%20better%20price%20on%20a%20repair!" class="ipad-price-match-btn">
            Check If We Can Match Your Price
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="ipad-cost-card">
          <div class="ipad-cost-icon-wrapper">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><path d="M3 12a9 9 0 1 0 9-9 9.75 9.75 0 0 0-6.74 2.74L3 8"/><path d="M3 3v5h5"/><path d="M12 7v5l4 2"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="ipad-cost-title">Lower Your iPad Repair Cost With a Trade-In</h3>
          <p class="ipad-cost-body">Trade in phones, tablets, consoles, or laptops — even broken ones — to reduce today's repair cost.</p>
          <p class="ipad-cost-note">Get paid via Cash, E-Transfer, or Store Credit</p>
          <a href="/trade-in" class="ipad-trade-in-btn">
            Lower My iPad Repair Cost &rarr;
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="ipad-pricing-context">
        <p class="ipad-context-paragraph">iPad repair costs depend heavily on the model and the type of screen — an iPad 9th Gen uses a standard LCD assembly that is significantly less expensive to repair than an iPad Pro M4 which uses a tandem OLED ProMotion display. <a href="https://support.apple.com/en-ca/111901" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="ipad-context-link">Apple's iPad repair service documentation</a> outlines warranty coverage and what to expect from out-of-warranty repairs.</p>
        <p class="ipad-context-paragraph">Many customers are surprised that an iPad Pro screen replacement can approach or exceed the cost of a new standard iPad. <a href="https://www.ifixit.com/Search?query=ipad+teardown" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="ipad-context-link">iFixit's iPad teardowns</a> show exactly why — the adhesive-sealed fused glass assemblies in Pro models require precision disassembly under heat and magnification, making them more labour-intensive than standard tablet repairs.</p>
        <p class="ipad-context-paragraph">If your iPad repair cost approaches its current resale value, we'll tell you honestly — and walk you through alternatives including data transfer to a new device or trade-in options toward a newer model. We'd rather give you the right advice than take your money for a repair that doesn't make financial sense.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
